# Email Configuration for Portfolio Website
# Replace nodemailer with Resend for better security

# 1. Sign up at https://resend.com (free tier available)
# 2. Get your API key from the dashboard
# 3. Create a .env file in your project root with:

RESEND_API_KEY=re_your_api_key_here
CONTACT_EMAIL=your-email@example.com
PORT=3000

# Benefits of Resend over nodemailer:
# - More secure (no password storage)
# - Better deliverability
# - Modern API
# - Free tier available
# - Better error handling
# - No need to configure SMTP settings

# IMPORTANT: Replace 'your-email@example.com' with your actual email address
# This email will receive contact form submissions 